CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 14, 1945, p. 13, reads: "Beauty on the Beach - Shapely Minnie Henderson of Warble Street shows what the smart lass will do on these smouldering days...take to the beach or pool.  She realy [really] adds to the scenery.  Take it easy, boys, she was just graduated from Peabody High School. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Minnie Henderson in two-piece bathing suit standing beside swimming pool and fountain in front of chain link fence
